Package com.worldbiomusic.minigameworld.minigameframes

Class MiniGame

java.lang.Object
com.worldbiomusic.minigameworld.minigameframes.MiniGame
Direct Known Subclasses:
SoloBattleMiniGame, SoloMiniGame, TeamBattleMiniGame, TeamMiniGame
public abstract class MiniGame extends Object
MiniGame class of all minigames
- Custom minigame frame can be made with extending this class
- Message only send to same minigame players

    • handleException

      public final void handleException​(MiniGameExceptionEvent exception)
      - Handle exception
      - If player exception
      - calls handleGameException(com.worldbiomusic.minigameworld.customevents.minigame.MiniGameExceptionEvent)
      - player will leave the game
      - checks MiniGameSetting.GameFinishCondition

      - If server exception
      - minigame will be finished
      Parameters:
      exception - Minigame exception
      See Also:
      MiniGameExceptionEvent
